Name: Skybox3D
About the game: CS:GO match replay and analysis software used by the top professional Counterstrike teams and tournaments around the world. Skybox3D provides a unique match replay experience that gives you the insight and analysis to help you improve as a player and as a team. Some key features include: View maps from anywhere and any angle Instantly move back and forth through rounds Turn buildings to glass ('Glassify') Track player paths and actions View the POV of any player .... and much more
